OL,3,CJersey mother calls for clarity over
OL,4,Cisland's dyslexia support
OL,6,FA Jersey mother has described her
OL,7,Fson's dyslexia diagnosis by an
OL,8,Feducational psychologist as "gold
OL,9,Fdust" amid fears these support
OL,10,Fservices are becoming more and more
OL,11,Fstretched in the island.
OL,13,FNaomi Bidmead praises the support and
OL,14,Ffunding her 13-year-old son Harry has
OL,15,Fhad since he was diagnosed with the
OL,16,Fcondition, even though it took nine
OL,17,Fyears to receive a diagnosis.
