OL,3,CJersey mother calls for clarity over
OL,4,Cisland's dyslexia support
OL,6,FNaomi told ITV News: "For us, the
OL,7,Feducational psychologist was
OL,8,Fincredibly important because they had
OL,9,Fall the bits of information that you
OL,10,Fneed and at the moment schools are
OL,11,Fcrying out for appointments with
OL,12,Feducational psychologists.
OL,14,F"They're gold dust."
OL,16,FThe Association of Educational
OL,17,FPsychologists (AEP), which provides
OL,18,Fsupport for diagnoses like Harry's by
OL,19,Fworking with schools, are currently in
OL,20,Fdispute with the States of Jersey,
OL,21,Fputting their services at risk.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
