OL,3,CJersey mother calls for clarity over
OL,4,Cisland's dyslexia support
OL,6,FIn a statement, the AEP said: "This
OL,7,Funfortunate situation has arisen due
OL,8,Fto the failure of the employer to deal
OL,9,Fappropriately with matters raised by
OL,10,FEducational Psychologists in the
OL,11,Fcourse of their work.
OL,13,F"AEP officials will continue to work
OL,14,Fwith senior officers to resolve the
OL,15,Fmatters which have led to this dispute.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
