OL,3,CJersey mother calls for clarity over
OL,4,Cisland's dyslexia support
OL,6,F"Until the dispute is lifted, the AEP
OL,7,Fcannot recommend Jersey as an
OL,8,Fappropriate or safe place for members
OL,9,Fto work and the AEP will not carry any
OL,10,Fadverts for the States of Jersey at
OL,11,Fthis time."
OL,13,FNaomi is anxious about the lack of
OL,14,Fsupport schools will now be given to
OL,15,Fhelp the most vulnerable pupils.
