OL,3,CJersey mother calls for clarity over
OL,4,Cisland's dyslexia support
OL,6,FShe said: "Without having the reports
OL,7,F(from the AEP), the teachers are
OL,8,Fworking with no information and the
OL,9,Fschools are being expected to meet
OL,10,Fdemands that they are not financially
OL,11,Fable to meet because they need more
OL,12,Fstaff and they need more training to
OL,13,Fmeet those demands.
OL,15,F"We talk about child-centred education
OL,16,Fbut that is the key to children having
OL,17,Fself-esteem."
