OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F388A1730967176
OL,3,CJersey mother calls for clarity over
OL,4,Cisland's dyslexia support
OL,6,F"It was deeply worrying to read the
OL,7,FAssociation of Educational
OL,8,FPsychologists' comments regarding
OL,9,FJersey, and I will be writing to the
OL,10,FMinister for Education to seek further
OL,11,Finformation on this issue and his
OL,12,Fassurance that he will be addressing
OL,13,Fthe Association's concerns as a matter
OL,14,Fof urgency.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
