OL,3,CJersey mother calls for clarity over
OL,4,Cisland's dyslexia support
OL,6,F"All children in Jersey have a right
OL,7,Fto an education that supports their
OL,8,Fintellectual, social and emotional
OL,9,Fgrowth and development. However,
OL,10,Fchildren with additional needs often
OL,11,Ffind education difficult to fully
OL,12,Faccess and enjoy.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
